Feature: all in one

  Scenario: create any object in one step
    When create
    """
    商品: {
      name: book
      color: red
    }

    品类: | id | name |
          | C1 | it   |
          | C2 | xx   |
    """
    Then all "商品" should:
    """
    : | name | color |
      | book | red   |
    """
    Then all "品类" should:
    """
    : | id | name |
      | C1 | it   |
      | C2 | xx   |
    """

  Scenario: create duplicated spec
    When create
    """
    商品: {
      name: book
      color: red
    }

    商品: | name   | color |
          | iphone | white |
    """
    Then all "商品" should:
    """
    : | name   | color |
      | book   | red   |
      | iphone | white |
    """

  Scenario: create with trait
    When create
    """
    商品(红色的): {
      name: book
    }
    商品(红色的): | name |
                   | PC   |
    """
    Then all "商品" should:
    """
    : | name | color |
      | book | red   |
      | PC   | red   |
    """

  Scenario: create with trait and without property
    When create
    """
    商品(红色的)
    商品(红色的)
    """
    Then all "商品" should:
    """
    : | color |
      | red   |
      | red   |
    """

